One of the most [[epic]] threads on [[Jewgrounds]]. Usually the most controversial all over the site, causing an instant [[lulz]] on all [[faggots|users]]. It's technically a Newgrounds [[forced meme]], as being a thread of [[over nine thousand|millions]] of posts [[copypasta|writing]] "Why is there a huge [[cock]] on the top left corner?"

[[Image:Cock thread.JPG|thumb|right|This is how it all started, notice the [[penis|arm]] on the top left corner.]]

==[[Shit nobody cares about|Beginning]]==
The [[shitstorm|thread]] started [[at least 100 years ago]] when a kid posted a pic of himself [[fail|giving the camera the finger so he could lengthen his e-peen]]. Another [[faggot|user]] quickly noticed the OP's friend's [[penis|arm]] in the top left corner of the pic and asked "Why is there a huge cock on the top left corner?" Other users then followed suit, [[troll|trolling]] him by repeating the same shit over and over.

Still, nobody knows the answer to WHY IS THERE A HUGE COCK ON THE TOP LEFT CORNER?

The original thread has been found here, if anyone wants to see it [[for the lulz]]: http://www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/487316

